  "body": "Currently the LES spec under [`Status (0x00)`](https://github.com/ethereum/devp2p/blob/master/caps/les.md#status-0x00) says:\r\n\r\n> `\"networkId\"` `P`: should be 0 for testnet, 1 for mainnet.\r\n\r\nThis doesn't seem correct, should the `networkId` be the `chainId` as specified by [EIP-155](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-155#list-of-chain-ids) /  [chainid.network](https://chainid.network/) ?",
